We managed to get the field into the request, but it gets sent to the server with the CDATA being XML-encoded:

    &lt;data&gt;&amp;lt;![CDATA[&amp;lt;?xml version=....
      &amp;lt;CheckData&amp;gt;
        ...
      &amp;lt;/CheckData&amp;gt;
